item.dc:creator: @Starting_up Starting up ...
item.description:
@Starting_up wrote:

[quote=“atrox_, post:9, topic:300244”][quote author=Starting up … link=topic=396534.msg2945206#msg2945206 date=1252182888]
Questions. I failed 10

1. Have you ever had an account at What.cd before?
2. Have you ever interviewed for a What.cd account before, and if so, by who and when?
3. Is English your first language? If not, tell me now and I will try to be more patient.
4. What is your email address? (not Hotmail)
5. Where are you located? (City / Country)
6. Why do you want to join What.cd?
7. Where did you hear about this IRC channel? (provide a link if possible; this is for market research purposes only)
8. What is the difference between a lossless codec and a lossy codec?
9. Put the following in order from LOWEST to HIGHEST average bitrate: 320kbps CBR MP3, V0 MP3, FLAC, 160kbps CBR MP3, V2 MP3 (-- you have 2 minutes to answer this question --)
10. Type my name so I know that you are done.
[/quote]

thats all the questions?[/quote]The first set up questions.
